# Gradle Build Conventions

## Build Commands

```bash
./gradlew assembleDebug          # Build debug APK
./gradlew assembleRelease       # Build release APK
./gradlew test                  # Run unit tests
./gradlew testDebugUnitTest     # Single test: --tests "com.personal.aurachat.MyTest"
./gradlew connectedAndroidTest   # Instrumented tests (device/emulator required)
./gradlew lint                  # Android lint checks
./gradlew clean                 # Clean build outputs
```

## Dependency Versions

- All versions centralized in `gradle/libs.versions.toml`
- Update versions there only; never inline in build files
